---
title: Cheesy Beef Rissoles & Roast Veggie Toss with Caramelised Balsamic & Mustard Onions
description: Rissoles are a crowd-pleasing dinner, but when you make them cheesy and cover them with tangy balsamic-mustard onions, they’re even harder to refuse! This colourful plate also gets a serve of roasted veggies for a rainbow of delights.
